trans-unit.source: Accesses XAML files that define types (with <xref uid="langword_csharp_x:Class" name="x:Class" href=""></xref>) and generates the corresponding source code that can be compiled into an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Ansluter till XAML-filer som definierar typer (med <xref uid="langword_csharp_x:Class" name="x:Class" href=""> </xref>) och genererar motsvarande källkoden som kan sammanställas till en sammansättning.

trans-unit.source: The XAML files processed by this task define new types as well as instantiate those types.
trans-unit.target: XAML-filer bearbetas av den här uppgiften definierar nya typer samt skapa en instans av dessa typer.

trans-unit.source: The PartialClassGenerationTask class reads in the new type definitions and generates source code files.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PartialClassGenerationTask läser i nya typdefinitioner och genererar källkodsfiler.

trans-unit.source: In addition, it generates a XAML file that contains the markup that instantiates the newly generated types.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom skapas en XAML-fil som innehåller koden som instantierar nyligen skapade typer.

trans-unit.source: This task should not be used to consume untrusted XAML inputs.
trans-unit.target: Den här uppgiften ska inte användas för att använda obetrodda XAML-indata.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.PartialClassGenerationTask"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.PartialClassGenerationTask"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether this project requires executing the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.CompilationPass2Task"></xref> task.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om det här projektet kräver den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.CompilationPass2Task"> </xref> aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: While processing the XAML files, the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.PartialClassGenerationTask> looks for unresolved types.
trans-unit.target: Under bearbetning av XAML-filer i <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.PartialClassGenerationTask>söker efter omatchade typer.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.PartialClassGenerationTask>

trans-unit.source: If it finds any, it launches the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.CompilationPass2Task> that compiles all of the XAML files in the project and checks to make sure all types are resolved.
trans-unit.target: Om den hittar någon startar den <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.CompilationPass2Task>som kompilerar alla XAML-filer i projektet och kontroll av att alla typer är lösta.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Xaml.CompilationPass2Task>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if there are unresolved types; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om det finns olösta typer. Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
